Valkyrie Profile 2: Silmeria:

I saw this game in flee market around a year ago. It was also dirty cheap, like under 5€ so I decided do buy it. 💰 I thought this game is some basic JRPG stuff, but it actually has pretty neat features and systems. ⚙️⚙️ Let's talk about those a little bit. 

Dungeon exploration has made in this game as 2D platforming! And that's first cool, unique feature. 💎 You can go right, left and jump ofc... But you can also walk into these mystical smoky things and if you do - Combat starts. ⚔️ I try to explain that later. 

You can also turn these smoky things to crystals. 💎 You can push these crystal or even use those as teleport. So these dungeons has tiny puzzles where you need to figure out how you supposed to move these crystals so you can go on. 💎 

I rly like this 2D system in this role-playing game. It makes this game more unique for sure. 🤔🤔 Atleast for me?

I also like the combat mode! Combat happens in 3D, in small arenas. ⚔️ Combat itself reminds me of Dynasty Warrior games, but you have smaller arenas etc. 🤔 You are fighting with four characters at ones, you have your action points and there's different kind a creatures around the arena. ⚔️ Combat is fun, innovative and full of action. 💥 Very nice features as well, but hard to explain. 🤐

And this game is role-playing game, so ofc you can gain levels, get better weapons etc basic Square Enix stuff. ⭐️

I haven't finished this one, and I rarely care about any stories so here's basically all I have right now. 🤔🤔

This game feels fresh to me! And I like it, even it's role-playing game. Check these features out and considering to buy it after that. 🤘🤘

Burning Force:

I bet many retrogamers here in Instagram have played or heard about game called - Space Harrier! 🐲
And boy that SEGA Saturn version of the game is pure gold, I love it. 💙

But have you ever played this game? Burning Force. 💫 This game is released by Namco but it definitely reminds me of Space Harrier witch is released by SEGA. 💙 Well that's not the point and I don't care it. If game developers wouldn't copy anything from each others, we would have like four different game series etc... 

The point was that if you like Namco and Space Harrier, you might like this game. 🤔🤔 So ye this game is third-person arcade style shooter, where you are riding on a futuristic bike. But before every boss level your airbike turns into flying ship that gives little bit variety for the game. 💫 Bca now you can fly also up and down you know. ☁️☁️ I like that idea and it works. 👍 You also get some unnecessary hints how to kill next boss. 💥 

First thing, I wanted to buy this game bca I love Space Harrier, but I mean look at that cover art. 😍🤤 So hot and at the time it was definitely futuristic. 😁 

Gameplay works nice for me. I had no problem with controls and game is simple to understand. Just shoot to kill. 💥 Collect power ups sometimes, and use your missiles. Avoid enemies and their projectiles. 👍 Simple arcade style shooter. 

Game has nice variety of different levels and that actually surprised me a little bit. 🌊 Soundtrack of this game aren't fantastic, but still okey. 🎵

Overall game is nice, but not even close as fun as Space Harrier. Although my Space Harrier is for Saturn and this game is for Mega Drive. 🤔 If you own both systems go for Space Harrier. Japan version of that game is very cheap. 😍😍

Riders Republic:

Are you guys ready for bumpy ride? Lean back and get focused, it's time to go fast and downhill. 🚲 

I saw short clip of this game in YouTube and I decided to buy it right away. ✅️ It looked so cool and extreme. 🪂 Well is this game as good as though, or even better? Here is my thoughts. 🚲

First things first! I have dreaming to be able to try downhill biking. 🚲 Those adrenaline rushes. 😤🔥 In my situation this game has to do it. 😅 So downhill biking was my main reasons to buy this. And I would be happy with it, but game also have other extreme sports, like snowboarding and bit weird jetpack sky flying and more. 🤔

I think game kinda sufferers bca it has different sport events. 🤔 And it might be better if it would be all about downhill biking. 🚲 But I get it. Everybody doesn't like biking as much. 
My girlfriend was fan of snowboarding part of the game for example!

Gameplay and different events kinda feels the same, but I like how fast and smooth it feels. 🚲 And I get small adrenaline rushes while playing it. 🔥Game looks very beautiful and realistic. 🌲 And I love that you can play it in first person view as well. 🤘 I have many new games to show to my friends, but this one will be the next.

I don't like those unnecessary story elements, what they tried to put into it. And game has too much talking about this and that... That really kills the adrenaline rush for sure. 😵‍💫 Let me just play, plz.

And as I said, game looks nice and realistic. But it still have nice colors and humour. 🦖 Nice job IMO. 
It also has great music selection for sure. 🤘

Very nice game! It have some unnecessary stuff, but I would recommend it for any extreme sports fans. 🚲🤘 It kinda reminds me about SSX game series. With all those tricks and tasks you can complete while playing it. 

Very cool game IMO. 🤘🤘

Milon's Secret Castle:

I never had this game, when I was kid, so I watched some footage of it and I thought it looked kinda fun. 😁 So I bought it, it was cheap. This game is developed and published by Hudson Soft. 💪 And they have made amazing games like Bomberman. 🤘

So! Does this game have same quality as Bomberman games? Let's see. 🤔

In this puzzly action game you are playing Sandman looking character Milon. 🧙‍♂️ Doesn't just look like a some kind of wizard, he can also shoot bubbles from his hands. 🔮 Mby he is some kinda shampoo-wizard? 🧼 

Anyhow! Running and jumping feels a bit the same that we have in Super Mario Bros 1. But levels are more like vertical mazes, that are full of secrets. 💰 Unfortunately these secrets are very stupidly hard to find or noticed... You need to shoot bubbles all over the place, and hope you hit something. 🧼 And that is just stupid. 🤯 Plus you has to find most of these secrets, or you can't go forward. 🤯

That's not the only problem in this game. Its easy to die in this game, and creatures are spawning from nowhere all the time. 😵 That's would be okey, but there's no extra lifes or continues!! Are you kidding me. 🤯 Most frustrating stuff ever. 

So yes I do not like this game. ☠️

Visually game has some charm, but that's about it. 🧙‍♂️
